The other sheet is a plan of
Angkor Wat, 13th, 14th century

00:33:45.030 --> 00:33:50.010
city in Cambodia,
which I want to use

00:33:50.010 --> 00:33:55.320
as an illustration of the
conjunction between built

00:33:55.320 --> 00:33:59.010
form associated with
religion, built form also

00:33:59.010 --> 00:34:03.880
at the same time serving
practical purposes.

00:34:03.880 --> 00:34:10.860
The feng shui in China
faces houses to the south.

00:34:10.860 --> 00:34:16.320
You are the lady who knows
more about China than I do.

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:21.179
Feng shui is a mystical
system for the selection

00:34:21.179 --> 00:34:26.850
of the site for the
location of buildings

00:34:26.850 --> 00:34:33.719
which, practically speaking,
faces in the right direction.

00:34:33.719 --> 00:34:36.630
Feng shui would be
